description:
The Revelation is the third studio album by Japanese rock band coldrain, released on April 17, 2013.

The album was also released by Hopeless Records on June 23, 2014 in Europe and on June 24, 2014 in North America. On August 8, 2014 it was released by Sony Music in Australia

